<module>
    <h>sgoil</h>
    <p><g>sgoil</g>
        <en>a school</en> is a feminine <a href="?xx=nouns/simple_common_nouns">simple common
        noun</a>.</p>

    <section>
        <h>adjectives</h>
        <p><g>sgoil</g> can be the (deep) subject of certain <a href="?xx=adjectives/adjectives"
            >adjectives</a>.</p>
        <module id="sgoil_mhoor">
            <h>sgoil mhór</h>
            <p><g>sgoil <a href="?gd=moor">mhór</a></g>
                <en>a big school</en> – <xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd>A bheil an sgoil mór? Tha.</gd>
                        <tr>Is the school big? Yes, it is.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 14</ref>
                    </li>
                </xl></p>
        </module>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h>prepositions</h>
        <section>
            <h>object</h>
            <p><g>sgoil</g> can be the object of certain <a href="?xx=prepositions/prepositions"
                >prepositions</a>.</p>
            <module id="ann_an_sgoil">
                <h>... ann an sgoil</h>
                <p><g>... <a href="?gd=an^preposition">ann an</a> sgoil</g>
                    <en>... in a school</en>. </p>
                <module>
                    <h>[duine] ann an sgoil</h>
                    <p><g>[duine] ann an sgoil</g>
                        <en>[a person] in a school</en> – <xl>
                            <li>
                                <gd>Cha robh a’ chaileag bheag anns an sgoil.</gd>
                                <tr>The little girl was not in the school.</tr>
                                <ref text="617">td. 15 [228]</ref>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <gd>A bheil Seònaid anns an sgoil an diugh? Chan eil.</gd>
                                <tr>Is Janet in the school today? No, she isn’t.</tr>
                                <ref text="617">td. 14</ref>
                            </li>
                        </xl>
                    </p>
                </module>
            </module>
        </section>
    </section>
    
